{
  "title": "Tangy Dense Korean Apple Stir-fry",
  "description": "This tangy and dense apple stir-fry is low-calorie-friendly and can help cure hangovers. Made with Braeburn apples, this dish features a unique blend of savory and sweet flavors.",
  "cuisine": "Korean",
